rmation from\none reference frame (linear or surface) to the other. In other words, the\nmethodology developed aims to make linear and surfacegeographic data\ninteroperable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Sep 2022 17:36:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-15"}
