uring full coherence,\nand non-negativity of the reconciled forecasts, the results show that for the\nconsidered dataset, cross-temporal forecast reconciliation significantly\nimproves on the sequential procedures proposed by Yagli et al. (2019), at any\ncross-sectional level of the hierarchy and for any temporal granularity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2022 08:56:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-16"}
