ically related groups, a more systematic treatment of lithology mixtures,\nand the chondrite/achondrite transition can further simplify the nomenclature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2022 15:44:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-16"}
